}, {"text": "(2)", "bbox": [85.5, 995.3, 115.0, 1018.4]}, {"text": "Represents the increase or decrease in reported amounts resulting from changes in exchange rates from those in effect", "bbox": [151.1, 995.3, 1138.0, 1018.4]}, {"text": "in the comparable prior year period for operating results.", "bbox": [151.1, 1020.3, 624.0, 1043.4]}, {"text": "Non-GAAP Financial Measures", "bbox": [110.5, 1074.5, 376.7, 1097.5]}, {"text": "Regulation G, Conditions for Use of Non-GAAP Financial Measures, and other SEC regulations define and prescribe the", "bbox": [135.5, 1109.9, 1150.6, 1133.0]}, {"text": "conditions for use of certain non-GAAP financial information. Our measures of “Free cash flow,” operating expenses with and", "bbox": [85.5, 1134.9, 1146.0, 1158.0]}, {"text": "without stock-based compensation, and the effect of exchange rates on our consolidated statements of operations, meet the", "bbox": [85.5, 1159.9, 1112.4, 1183.0]}, {"text": "definition of non-GAAP financial measures.", "bbox": [85.5, 1184.9, 454.6, 1208.0]}, {"text": "Free cash flow is used in addition to and in conjunction with results presented in accordance with GAAP and free cash", "bbox": [135.5, 1228.7, 1128.5, 1251.8]}, {"text": "flow should not be relied upon to the exclusion of GAAP financial measures.", "bbox": [85.5, 1253.7, 727.8, 1276.8]}, {"text": "Free cash flow, which we reconcile to “Net cash provided by (used in) operating activities,” is cash flow from operations", "bbox": [135.5, 1297.5, 1148.2, 1320.5]}, {"text": "reduced by “Purchases of property and equipment, including internal-use software and website development,” which are", "bbox": [85.5, 1322.5, 1095.5, 1345.5]}, {"text": "included in cash flow from investing activities. We use free cash flow, and ratios based on it, to conduct and evaluate our", "bbox": [85.5, 1347.5, 1097.8, 1370.5]}, {"text": "business because, although it is similar to cash flow from operations, we believe it typically will present a more conservative", "bbox": [85.5, 1372.5, 1130.9, 1395.6]}, {"text": "measure of cash flow from operations since purchases of property and equipment, including internal-use software and website", "bbox": [85.5, 1397.5, 1142.4, 1420.6]}, {"text": "development, are a necessary component of ongoing operations.", "bbox": [85.5, 1422.5, 620.9, 1445.6]}, {"text": "Free cash flow has limitations due to the fact that it does not represent the residual cash flow available for discretionary", "bbox": [135.5, 1466.3, 1136.3, 1489.3]}, {"text": "expenditures. For example, free cash flow does not incorporate the portion of payments representing principal reductions of", "bbox": [85.5, 1491.3, 1122.1, 1514.3]}, {"text": "debt, property and equipment acquired under capital leases and other leases accounted for as financing arrangements, or cash", "bbox": [85.5, 1516.3, 1133.0, 1539.4]}]}